    "text": "Fig. 1. Detection of the binding between the two partners of a specific complex. (A) High-mass MALDI mass spectrum of the bPrP and an antibody, 1ES, against bPrP without cross-linking. (B) Detection of the [15·bPrP] and [IE5®2bPrP] complexes after cross-linking. (C) Sensorgram of binding and dissociation between the immobilized ligand, 1ES, and the analyte, bPrP. The beginning of the sensorgram shows the level of response from the surface with only 1E5, the middle section shows the binding of bPrP with the surface during the injection, and the last section corresponds to the dissociation of",
